{
  "stem": "5328.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you had-- I think they gave us the meals on the-- on the bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to eat on the bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't a big boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a transport boat--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were on the boat from-- we went from-- from France, from Lyon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was about two weeks we were on the boat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in Cyprus for-- until I gave birth to my eldest daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it was a quota to come to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were from the first quota with the-- the parents with the children,  with the babies, were the first quota.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- we were in the first quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a little-- not-- not much longer, Israel became a state.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we already were occupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we came to Israel, we were in a DP camp, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They brought us in a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had a cousin in-- in Petah Tikva-- not my cousin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a relative.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That he was in Israel for a long time already, from the halutzim in the '20s, that he went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I knew just his name, and I knew he's in Petah Tikva.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's all I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my husband, you watch the baby, and I'm going to go to Petah Tikva and-- and look for [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he-- that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to Petah Tikva just knowing the name-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very hot, and I wanted to drink a glass of water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ask them-- in Hebrew, because I knew Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not as good as now, but-- from school that I learned.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
